#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.43"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.43:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.43:0.2"
msgid "5. Muṇḍarājavagga"
msgstr "5. With King Muṇḍa"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: pañcaiṭṭhadhammasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.43:0.3"
msgid "43. Iṭṭhasutta"
msgstr "43. Likable"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho "
"anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat "
"down to one side. The Buddha said to him:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:2.1"
msgid "“Pañcime, gahapati, dhammā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā dullabhā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, these five things that are likable, desirable, and agreeable "
"are hard to get in the world."

msgctxt "an5.43:2.2"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.43:2.3"
msgid "Āyu, gahapati, iṭṭho kanto manāpo dullabho lokasmiṃ;"
msgstr "Long life,"

msgctxt "an5.43:2.4"
msgid "vaṇṇo iṭṭho kanto manāpo dullabho lokasmiṃ;"
msgstr "beauty,"

msgctxt "an5.43:2.5"
msgid "sukhaṃ iṭṭhaṃ kantaṃ manāpaṃ dullabhaṃ lokasmiṃ;"
msgstr "happiness,"

msgctxt "an5.43:2.6"
msgid "yaso iṭṭho kanto manāpo dullabho lokasmiṃ;"
msgstr "fame,"

msgctxt "an5.43:2.7"
msgid "saggā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā dullabhā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "and heaven."

msgctxt "an5.43:2.8"
msgid "Ime kho, gahapati, pañca dhammā iṭṭhā kantā manāpā dullabhā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"These are the five things that are likable, desirable, and agreeable, but "
"hard to get in the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.48"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: patthanāhetu vā → na patthanahetu vā (s1-3, km) | na patthanāhetu vā (pts1)
msgctxt "an5.43:3.1"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, gahapati, pañcannaṃ dhammānaṃ iṭṭhānaṃ kantānaṃ manāpānaṃ "
"dullabhānaṃ lokasmiṃ na āyācanahetu vā patthanāhetu vā paṭilābhaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""
"And I say that these five things are not got by praying or wishing for them."

msgctxt "an5.43:3.2"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, gahapati, pañcannaṃ dhammānaṃ iṭṭhānaṃ kantānaṃ manāpānaṃ "
"dullabhānaṃ lokasmiṃ āyācanahetu vā patthanāhetu vā paṭilābho abhavissa, ko "
"idha kena hāyetha?"
msgstr "If they were, who would lack them?"

# Accepting BB’s reading “vā pihetuṃ”.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:4.1"
msgid ""
"Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako āyukāmo āyuṃ āyācituṃ vā abhinandituṃ "
"vā āyussa vāpi hetu."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who wants to live long ought not pray for it, or delight in "
"it, or pine for it."

msgctxt "an5.43:4.2"
msgid ""
"Āyukāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena āyusaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā."
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to long life."

msgctxt "an5.43:4.3"
msgid "Āyusaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā āyupaṭilābhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain long life"

msgctxt "an5.43:4.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti āyussa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā."
msgstr "as a god or a human being."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:5.1"
msgid ""
"Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako vaṇṇakāmo vaṇṇaṃ āyācituṃ vā "
"abhinandituṃ vā vaṇṇassa vāpi hetu."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who wants to be beautiful ought not pray for it, or delight "
"in it, or pine for it."

msgctxt "an5.43:5.2"
msgid ""
"Vaṇṇakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena vaṇṇasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā "
"paṭipajjitabbā."
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to beauty."

msgctxt "an5.43:5.3"
msgid "Vaṇṇasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā vaṇṇapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain beauty"

msgctxt "an5.43:5.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti vaṇṇassa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā."
msgstr "as a god or a human being."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:6.1"
msgid ""
"Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako sukhakāmo sukhaṃ āyācituṃ vā "
"abhinandituṃ vā sukhassa vāpi hetu."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who wants to be happy ought not pray for it, or delight in "
"it, or pine for it."

msgctxt "an5.43:6.2"
msgid ""
"Sukhakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena sukhasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā "
"paṭipajjitabbā."
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to happiness."

msgctxt "an5.43:6.3"
msgid "Sukhasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā sukhapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain happiness"

msgctxt "an5.43:6.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti sukhassa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā."
msgstr "as a god or a human being."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:7.1"
msgid ""
"Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako yasakāmo yasaṃ āyācituṃ vā "
"abhinandituṃ vā yasassa vāpi hetu."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who wants to be famous ought not pray for it, or delight in "
"it, or pine for it."

msgctxt "an5.43:7.2"
msgid ""
"Yasakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena yasasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā paṭipajjitabbā."
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to fame."

msgctxt "an5.43:7.3"
msgid "Yasasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā yasapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain fame"

msgctxt "an5.43:7.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti yasassa dibbassa vā mānusassa vā."
msgstr "as a god or a human being."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:8.1"
msgid ""
"Na kho, gahapati, arahati ariyasāvako saggakāmo saggaṃ āyācituṃ vā "
"abhinandituṃ vā saggānaṃ vāpi hetu."
msgstr ""
"A noble disciple who wants to go to heaven ought not pray for it, or delight "
"in it, or pine for it."

msgctxt "an5.43:8.2"
msgid ""
"Saggakāmena, gahapati, ariyasāvakena saggasaṃvattanikā paṭipadā "
"paṭipajjitabbā."
msgstr "Instead, they should practice the way that leads to heaven."

msgctxt "an5.43:8.3"
msgid "Saggasaṃvattanikā hissa paṭipadā paṭipannā saggapaṭilābhāya saṃvattati."
msgstr "For by practicing that way they gain heaven,"

msgctxt "an5.43:8.4"
msgid "So lābhī hoti saggānanti."
msgstr "they are one who gains the heavens."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:9.1"
msgid "Āyuṃ vaṇṇaṃ yasaṃ kittiṃ,"
msgstr "For one who desires a continuous flow"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:9.2"
msgid "Saggaṃ uccākulīnataṃ;"
msgstr "of exceptional delights—"

#. <br>
#. VAR: patthayānena → patthayamānena (mr)
msgctxt "an5.43:9.3"
msgid "Ratiyo patthayānena,"
msgstr "long life, beauty, fame and reputation,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:9.4"
msgid "Uḷārā aparāparā."
msgstr "heaven, and birth in an eminent family—"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.49"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.1"
msgid "Appamādaṃ pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "the astute praise diligence"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.2"
msgid "puññakiriyāsu paṇḍitā;"
msgstr "in making merit."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.3"
msgid "Appamatto ubho atthe,"
msgstr "Being diligent, an astute person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:10.4"
msgid "adhigaṇhāti paṇḍito."
msgstr "secures both benefits:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
#. VAR: Diṭṭhe dhamme ca → diṭṭheva dhamme (bj)
msgctxt "an5.43:11.1"
msgid "Diṭṭhe dhamme ca yo attho,"
msgstr "the benefit in this life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:11.2"
msgid "yo cattho samparāyiko;"
msgstr "and in lives to come."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:11.3"
msgid "Atthābhisamayā dhīro,"
msgstr "A wise one, comprehending the meaning,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.43:11.4"
msgid "paṇḍitoti pavuccatī”ti."
msgstr "is called ‘astute’.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.43:11.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
